Akira Umeda.title: passagem
Akira Umeda.about: Tracks originally conceived and recorded for "Passagem", performance artwork by Reiko Shimizu which had a single presentation at the Department of Architecture/University of Taubaté, São Paulo SP Brazil in 1997. Reiko Shimizu suggested a soundtrack that simply resembled a heartbeat. Although intended to solely accompany this performance artwork, these tracks have been used in other ones over time. Original digital recordings lost. These digital versions taken from old and damaged cassette tape.
Akira Umeda.credits:
released February 11, 2021
Akira Umeda: electronics.
